releases.name: Quick and Cool
releases.body:
- modernise JS 🤓 
- don't load useless script ⏩ 
- add linter 🔗 
- OMS engines, not SSME during OMS-1 - 3 🚀 🙄

releases.name: I didn't forget about updating
releases.body:
1. compress videos 📹 🛩 
2. crop videos 🐊 
3. extra videos for
   - touchdown 🛬
   - samson 🐶 
   - frimout 🔭
4. optimise images 👌
5. update build tools 🆕
6. slightly more modern js 🆒 
7. overall smaller size (400 -> 100 MB) 😎

releases.name: Small but Powerful
releases.body:
- fix links in readme :pencil2: 
- allow time to be set :clock1: 
- invisible improvements 👓

releases.name: Super Release!
releases.body:
Features: 
- automatically poll the ISS every 10 seconds :rocket:
- slightly longer line being drawn :pencil:
- make header fit better on smaller displays :abcd:
- add all steps :walking: 
- allow step to be set from remote :registered: 
- better CONTRIBUTING.md :sun_with_face:

releases.name: Smart Viewer
releases.body:
Features:
- use `pre` for ticker :wink: 
- check properly for electron :open_mouth: 
- make the map update :rocket:
